 20000000      Monte-Carlo trials, 21.75M events will have 2G rzdat output file
        1      Spectrometer (1=HMS, 2=SHMS, 3=..)
   3400.0      Spectrometer momentum (in MeV/c)
     30.0      Spectrometer angle (in degrees)
    -16.0      M.C. DP/P  down limit 
     30.0      M.C. DP/P  up   limit 
    -75.0      M.C. dydz(phi) down limit (mr)
     75.0      M.C. dydz(phi) up   limit (mr)
