     85.0      M.C. dxdz(theta) up   limit (mr)
     0.01      Horiz beam spot size in cm (Full width of +/- 1 sigma)
     0.01      Vert  beam spot size in cm (Full width of +/- 1 sigma)
     70.0      Thickness of target (Full width, cm)
      0.3      Raster half-width x (cm)
      0.3      Raster half-width y (cm)
     50.0      DP/P  reconstruction cut (half width in % )
    100.0      Theta reconstruction cut (half width in mr)
    100.0      Phi   reconstruction cut (half width in mr)
     50.0      ZTGT  reconstruction cut (Half width in cm)
  44947.0      one radiation length of target material (in cm)
